sources.description:
Bigfoot Kills Anyone Who Sees It | Feet of Death | Bigfoot Full Movie

When a paranormal social media influencer, Chris, winds up dead, Jason a USFS Agent must grapple with the reality of the fact that Bigfoot might actually exist. The supposed mythical creature might even be responsible for a string of unusual deaths in his small town. Chris Dixon starts off investigating the murders at the base of Mt. Saint Helens for his online TV series, Myths of the Unknown, but winds up a casualty of his own investigation. Jason, a USFS ranger who has recently lost his wife is spiraling into depression when he is thrust head first into this mythological adventure. The story unfolds back and forth until their paths cross and Jason is left with a decision of whether to give up or dive deeper down the rabbit hole that is Sasquatch.

2024.  Stars: Andrew Jacob Brown, Jack Vanover, Benjamin Watts
